features.additionalInfo: Enjoy secure Online Business Banking at your fingertips. As a customer on this account you may also be entitled to apply for our Online Business Banking service. If you apply for that service you will be provided with a separate Product Disclosure Statement and your use of the service will be a matter of separate agreement with us. Separate fees are applicable for this service.

Link to an existing account you hold with any Australian financial institution. Withdrawals from your Business TeleNet Saver Account can only be made by Linked Account Transfer to your Linked Account against cleared funds.
View your account statements online at any time with eStatements.
The option to track your finances through data feeds to accounting software packages like Xero(TM) and MYOB(R).
24/7 In App Messaging - Why wait on hold. Message us and get a response in real-time.

constraints.additionalInfo: No minimum balance or ongoing deposit required.
To open your account, you'll need to make a minimum opening deposit of $1 from your linked transaction account.

eligibility.additionalValue: Sole trader, partnership, company, trust, super fund (including self managed super fund), society, strata or cooperative business types.
eligibility.additionalInfo: Your business type is a sole trader, partnership, company, trust, super fund (including self managed super fund), society, strata or cooperative.
The business was established and has tax residency in Australia.
You must nominate between one and four Authorised Users to operate the account.

Your linked account can be with Bankwest or any other financial institution in Australia. It must be held in exactly the same name as your Business TeleNet Saver, allow direct debits to and from the account, and cannot be a credit card account.

eligibility.additionalValue: Relationship managed customers only (limited exceptions may apply).
eligibility.additionalInfo: Only available to relationship managed customers (limited exceptions may apply).

data.name: Business TeleNet Saver
data.description: A savings account that lets you earn variable interest without having to lock your money away. It's available to sole traders, partnerships, companies, trusts, super funds (including SMSFs), societies, strata and cooperatives that were established and have tax residency in Australia.
